<div class="intro">
    <h1>Customize Komodo</h1>

    <p>
        Komodo is by far the most customizable IDE out there. It is built on top
        of the Mozilla framework, allowing it to be customized in nearly any way you
        wish.
    </p>

    <img src="/assets/images/layout/customizable.png" alt="Komodo is by far the most customizable IDE out there">

    <p>
        <strong>Did you know?</strong><br>
        Komodo is largely made up out of JavaScript,
        CSS and XUL (HTML for the Desktop).
    </p>
</div>

